{"product_id":"naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF 2-in-1 Shampoo \u0026 Conditioner for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e2-in-1 kids Shampoo \u0026amp; Conditioner for all hairtypes (long, short, thick or curly). The shampoo cleanses your hair while the anti-tangle formula ensures that the hair is soft and easy to comb through. Softens and detangles hair and hydrates with sunflower- and linseed oil. For all kids. Without SLES or microplastics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMild, fruity scent developed for and by children.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eTake a coin-sized amount of Naif 2-in-1 Shampoo and Conditioner and massage into wet hair. Leave it in for a bit, rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton) Seed Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Betaine, Inulin, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445993644359,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-851648.png?v=1739897337","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}